      "id": 262087,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "CVE-2022-35256 Detail\n\nDescription\nThe llhttp parser in the http module in Node v18.7.0 does not correctly handle header fields that are not terminated with CLRF. This may result in HTTP Request Smuggling.\n\nNVD Link: https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2022-35256\nHackerOne original submission: https://hackerone.com/reports/1675191",
